summary:
Always good to remember where you came from to see where you are now.
I always loved to draw and feel I've been doing it since I...
body:
Always good to remember where you came from to see where you are now.

I always loved to draw and feel I’ve been doing it since I can remember. But I only started to draw digitally in 2015. And getting used to the new medium was a big struggle first.

2015 ——————–> 2019
